                    licence, and indicate if changes were made.
  - NonCommercial — You may not use the material for commercial purposes.

Full legal text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/legalcode

### Note on the underlying literary work

ፍቅር እስከ መቃብር (Fikir Eske Mekabir) was written by Haddis Alemayehu and first
published in 1968.  The original literary text remains the intellectual property
of the Haddis Alemayehu estate and is protected by copyright.  The CC BY-NC 4.0
licence above applies solely to the OCR corrections, text formatting, and other
supplementary materials produced by this project — not to the underlying literary
work itself.

The source scan used as input was uploaded to the Internet Archive by
Fesseha Atlaw (ፍሥሓ አጥላው): https://archive.org/details/fikir

